    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through a crack in the wall, a mentor-inmate trades truths for wins, in a tile match game in which the loser is hit with a hammer on its hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/aa7a0b7e2a24a71a317e86546083a453.poster.avif?t=1771781261\" width=632 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/aa7a0b7e2a24a71a317e86546083a453.webm?t=1771781261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/aa7a0b7e2a24a71a317e86546083a453.mp4?t=1771781261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guiding you toward a final test where compliance, paradox, or defiance determines the cycle's future,  Velvet Hammer is a narrative-driven psychological thriller where the system turns play&quot; into punishment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/30f99b72a53d4a245f0a70f7f805f8ed.poster.avif?t=1771781261\" width=632 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/30f99b72a53d4a245f0a70f7f805f8ed.webm?t=1771781261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049800/extras/30f99b72a53d4a245f0a70f7f805f8ed.mp4?t=1771781261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 12 days</p>",
